{
  "description": "Cross-language conformance for the engine debrid resolve query. The host supplies sources, the user's debrid services, and the (infohash, service) pairs it knows are cached (from its hive vault); the engine returns the ordered resolve plan: rank 0 direct, 1 debrid-cached (instant), 2 debrid-uncached, 3 torrent, sorted by (rank, source_index). No network in the engine.",
